        |‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒‒
        !-->
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card">
                <h4 class="card-title">Add Jounrnal - Step One</h4>
                <div class="progress">
                    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="75" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 25%"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">

                        <form asp-action="SaveStepOne" asp-controller="Journal" method="post">

                            <div class="row">

                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <hr class="d-md-none">
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label>Date: </label><br />
                                        <div class="input-group  required">
                                            <input type="text" class="form-control date" placeholder="Date"   readonly/>
                                            <span class="input-group-addon">
                                                <i class="fa fa-calendar"></i>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>

                            <br class="clearfix" />
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <hr class="d-md-none">
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label>Description <span class="req">*</span></label>
                                        <textarea type="text" class="form-control" maxlenght="140" rows="6" required></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <br class="clearfix" />


                            <div class="row">

                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <hr class="d-md-none">
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label>Economic: </label>
                                        <select class="form-control" required>
                                            <option value="">-- Select Economic --</option>
                                            <option value="CONSTRUCTION/PROVISION OF MILITARY BARACKS">CONSTRUCTION/PROVISION OF MILITARY BARACKS</option>
                                            <option value="CONSTRUCTION/PROVISION OF DEFENCE EQUIPMENTS">CONSTRUCTION/PROVISION OF DEFENCE EQUIPMENTS</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>


                                <div class="col-md-4">
                                    <hr class="d-md-none">
                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <label>Fund <span class="req">*</span></label>
                                        <select class="form-control" required>
                                            <option value="">-- Select Fund  --</option>
                                            <option value="FAAC DIRECT ALLOCATION">FAAC DIRECT ALLOCATION</option>
                                            <option value="MAIN ENVELOP - BUDGETARY ALLOCATION">MAIN ENVELOP - BUDGETARY ALLOCATION</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <br class="clearfix" />

                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-8">
                                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-w-md btn-bold btn-primary pull-right">Next</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </form>
                        <br class="clearfix" /><br class="clearfix" /><br class="clearfix" /><br class="clearfix" />
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>





    </div>
</div><!--/.main-content -->
